<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ر ز ء<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٠٨٦ - ر ز ء]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رزَأَ يَرزَأ، رُزْءًا ورَزْءًا، فهو رازئ، والمفعول مَرْزوء<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• رزَأ الشَّخصَ:</span> أصابه بمصيبة.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• رزَأ مالَ شرِيكه:</span> أخذ منه شيئًا فنقصه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>